'''Children's International Film Festival''' has been conceptualised by The Film Studio FZ LLC, which is a company based out of [[Dubai Studio City]]. Children's International Film Festival, is commonly known as CIFF is UAE's first national level Children's Film Festival.<ref>{{cite web|title=Children’s international film festival in Dubai|url=http://arabia365.com/childrens-international-film-festival-in-dubai/|publisher=arabia365.com|accessdate=20 October 2014}}</ref> CIFF over a period of time has attracted significant attention from schools, parents, families & filmmakers - locally, regionally and globally.<ref>{{cite web|title=Children’s International Film Festival in Dubai|url=http://www.timeoutdubai.com/films/features/51530-childrens-international-film-festival-in-dubai|publisher=timeoutdubai.com|accessdate=20 October 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Children’s film festival opens today in the UAE|url=http://www.thenational.ae/blogs/scene-heard/childrens-film-festival-opens-today-in-the-uae|publisher=thenational.ae|accessdate=20 October 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Children’s International Film Festival (CIFF)|url=http://www.dubaicity.com/childrens-international-film-festival-ciff/|publisher=dubaicity.com|accessdate=20 October 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Children’s International Film Festival 2014 to Begin in UAE|url=http://enme.blouinartinfo.com/news/story/1025308/childrens-international-film-festival-2014-to-begin-in-uae|publisher=blouinartinfo.com|accessdate=20 October 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Children across UAE get thinking caps on for movie-making action|url=http://www.thenational.ae/uae/education/children-across-uae-get-thinking-caps-on-for-movie-making-action|publisher=thenational.ae|accessdate=20 October 2014}}</ref>
